---
title: Golden Fog Gate Skip
hidden: false
---
This skip refers to the golden fog leading to the [Duke's Archives](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/the-duke-s-archives); it allows the player to enter the Archives without having to place the [Lordvessel](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/lordvessel) at the [Firelink Altar](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/firelink-altar).\
\
There are two ways to perform this skip: one involves using a [deathcam](/darksouls/deathcam), while the other requires very precise movement on a ledge out of bounds.

## External resources

- Seamwalk method without bow tutorial ( extremely difficult ) [https://youtu.be/DPO4f66wx24?list=PLgswmMvZsZ1UmUU_DYlzIMaSyqDYOv57r](https://youtu.be/DPO4f66wx24?list=PLgswmMvZsZ1UmUU_DYlzIMaSyqDYOv57r) by aeiou on YouTube.
- Seamwalk method with bow ( very difficult ) [https://youtu.be/BMsKIWuhOsk?t=1911](https://youtu.be/BMsKIWuhOsk?t=1911) by Danflesh on YouTube.
- Deathcam Method ( easy ) [https://youtu.be/iDJ5KM3d7GQ](https://youtu.be/iDJ5KM3d7GQ) by **つーさんですよ** on YouTube.
